<p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--foreground); line-height: 1.6;">You wake up puffy. Your eyes are swollen, dark circles are prominent, and you look tired even though you slept eight hours. You've tried expensive serums, caffeine creams, and makeup hacks, but they don't actually address the root cause—fluid retention and inflammation under the eyes. Enter the Cooling Gel Eye Mask: a cold therapy solution that actually reduces puffiness and brightens your under-eye area in 20 minutes, no serums or needles required.</p>

